            <biogHist>
                <p>John Morrison was the son of Alexander Morrison, crofter, and Marion Morrison n√©e
                    Campbell. He married Ann MacKenzie and in the 1871 census there was four
                    children recorded living with them: Mary (20), Alexander (18), Marion (14) and
                    Norman (10). </p>
                <p>He died in 1888 and the cause of death recorded was old age and his son Alex
                    Morrison witnessed the certificate.</p>
                <p>Carmichael collected two stories from John Morrison entitled 'Loch Utramal' and
